Class SecurityGroupDeleteBOMImpl

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
BusinessObjectModule, DeleteBOM
public class SecurityGroupDeleteBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements DeleteBOM

This is the Delete Business Object Module implementation for a Security Group BOM. A Security Group BOM consists of the Security Group record and its associated Security Group SID records. This class deletes the specified Security Group BOM from the target system.
